      <div class="perf__feat"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--rose)" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2l2.6 5.3 5.8.8-4.2 4.1 1 5.8L12 15.4 6.8 18l1-5.8L3.6 8.1l5.8-.8z"/></svg><h4>Above-market performance</h4><p>Our homes out-earned the San Diego market on RevPAR every month of the season — consistently, not occasionally.</p></div>
      <div class="perf__feat"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--rose)" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 4h16v16H4z"/><path d="M8 10h8M8 14h5"/></svg><h4>Transparent accounting</h4><p>Itemized monthly statements — every payout and expense visible, no mystery fees, ever.</p></div>
      <div class="perf__feat"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--rose)" stroke-width="1.8" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M3 9h18M8 18v3M16 18v3"/></svg><h4>Owner dashboard</h4><p>A real-time portal for bookings, earnings, and owner stays — your numbers whenever you want them.</p></div>
    </div>
